{"tid":1457553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩各位散水撚同勇武入黎睇睇","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:31:10.000Z","uid":208092,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1df377626973eac1cac73ca6c34f5321aed8676c","tid":1457553,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"今日機場依家場面係柒婆同共狗最想睇到<br />\n點解？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第一</span> 不斷放風 制造白色恐怖 成功令一班係屋企既冷氣散水軍師驚真係會清場<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不斷叫人走 甚至去用一啲未經證實既消息去幫啲狗官不廢一兵一卒去令大部分人走</span></span> 令到我地自亂陣腳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第二</span> 唔好忘記初衷 要記返立法會義士講過啲咩 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要走一齊走 要留一齊留 同埋兄弟爬山 各自努力</span></span> 點解到依家做咩決定唔係俾前線決定呢 就算真係有鬼係入面都好 我相信唔多50人 我地既兄弟係多過啲鬼<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">100倍</span></span>呀 仲要今日係和理非 我相信前線一定可以做一個好好既決定 而唔係咁多位冷氣軍師比意見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第三</span> 今日有咁多消息同員工證 我有理由懷疑 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家啲員工證同消息都係狗放岀黎 目的係想我地將假既野當係真</span></span> 點解？因為一直以來我地一見到員工證就會低心入面就相信 會覺得一定係企我地依邊 但係唔好唔記得 依家狗隊換左人管理指揮 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做任何決定都係不擇手段 你越覺得無可能既野就越有可能 你覺得岀黎既人無鬼 就放隻鬼入去</span></span> 所以依家要做既野唔係要揾邊個係鬼 咁樣只會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">互相懷疑 到最後就會分化</span></span> 大家岀黎只要唔好行單 同互相照顧 一個手足被捉 就十個手足去救 咁樣內鬼就會廢左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第四</span> 擔心係無問題 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但唔係瘋狂叫人走叫人撤</span></span> 點解唔選擇講 邊到的到有狗 邊到邊到有消息講 前線留意下 有需要就全部一齊撤 唔好留低任何手足 咁講會唔會好啲呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第五 亦都係最重要 三個不 不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰</span></span> 有任何手足做錯講錯都好 我希望大家吸取教訓 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">改善下次行動</span></span> 而唔係淨係批評<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後 香港加油 我相信我地一定得 有能力再次望到我地既將來 </span></span>"},{"pid":"ba4f7d580a07a89327d537bad96fb091a02b86ad","tid":1457553,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:52:19.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"b87d7d73452fc3c6c4d976ebc1aa10dc8242614c","tid":1457553,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:52:29.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"bf8f233780313a4f8ef3194cc334aa1b4bdf4fdd","tid":1457553,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:52:39.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8a1a51c89bc249b2e1cca9ffdf7b0ceff2703805","tid":1457553,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:52:49.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"83d8cc09660b5fcee9fa4af5d266abc93c463812","tid":1457553,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"6ad2446756097c4fc61d167c493a43c492cefa19","tid":1457553,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:06.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"3a56471d2dcd01e7896581773faaf19cd238130c","tid":1457553,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:16.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"bc280def687e0070ad0b4afb29c15a5bb191cd98","tid":1457553,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:26.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"5cb85000e53ca5ec61a7d43dae9ded99f509acc1","tid":1457553,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"a55c85626839c64cc4e34e6d113b80412c347715","tid":1457553,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:46.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"f8019c75f705456fb4fcb08e2cf8fc3c5f2165ab","tid":1457553,"uid":138268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:54.000Z","msg":"對唔住今日柒咗"},{"pid":"9e55af